"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-music-music-news-dr-dre-snoop-dogg-olympic-ceremony-1235078730\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByTom\\u00e1s Mier  There is nothing likeDr.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 38, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"DreandSnoop Dogg's musical connection.\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 77, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview Monday, after thepair took the stageat a California beach as part of the ParisOlympics' closing ceremony, Dre spoke withEntertainment Tonightabout working with Snoop for the first time in 30 years on the rapper's upcoming album.\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 135, \"end\": 145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9999999934452717, \"rank\": 6.381807796797618e-09, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dre said that he produced the entire record, and provided vocals on a couple of songs (though he said he thinks only one will make the final cut).\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also teased the \\\"amazing roster of artists\\\" who feature on the record, though only revealed one name: Sting.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the long gap betweenDoggystyleand this new record -rumored to be titledMissionary- Dre said the pair are having more fun working together than ever.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were kids at that time, you know what I mean?\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop may have been like 18 or 19 years old and I am, I think, I am six years older than him,\\\" Dre said.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So we were kids at that time, and this one is gonna show a different level of maturity with his lyrics and with my music.\\\"\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like this is some of the best music I have done in my career,\\\" saidThe Chroniclegend.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, the pairstopped byJimmy Kimmel Live!and spoke about working together onMissionary.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1160, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Kimmel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.993877568662241e-23, \"text\": \"Kimmel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Kimmel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Kimmel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first album I have done with Snoop was in 1993 and it's the only album I have ever produced on Snoop,\\\" Dr. Dre said at the time.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So now, believe it or not, we are getting together again and we are almost done with the album.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first album was calledDoggystyle, so we decided to flip it and call this oneMissionary.\\\"\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During theEntertainment Tonightinterview, Dre also spoke about his love for performing alongside Snoop.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's magical.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not even feel comfortable performing without Snoop,\\\" Dre said.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Something about the synergy that me and Snoop have is really interesting.\\\"\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Really, Snoop, he's the superstar.\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the co-star when we get on stage,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's different when we are in the studio, you know?\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am the captain when we are in the studio, but when we go outside, Snoop is the guy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The new interview comes a day after Dre and Snoop performed from a beach in Southern California, alongside the Red Hot Chili Peppers and Billie Eilish, to commemorate the transition from the 2024 Olympics in Paris to the 2028 Olympic Games in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2291, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Hot Chili Peppers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}, {\"begin\": 2173, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billie_Eilish\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Billie Eilish\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billie_Eilish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billie_Eilish\"}, {\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992865014, \"rank\": 7.13590219448245e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2279, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.0799196513874892e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dre added that the Olympic Committee made sure that everything about their performance was \\\"handled\\\" with care, and kept a secret before it aired on NBC.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2441, \"end\": 2444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999993634082537, \"rank\": 4.465963654483652e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was wondering how they were gonna do that and nobody had cell phones or anything like that.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was filmed the day before it aired,\\\" Dre said.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So trying to keep that a secret for that amount of time seems like it would have been impossible, but they made it happen!\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Trending StoriesJohn Lithgow Knows J.K. Rowling's Anti-Trans Views Will Now Forever Come Up in 'Every Interview'Kevin Spacey's 'Mental Illness' Should Trigger $29.5 Million Payout, 'House of Cards' Trial Jurors HearBTS Nails Its Comeback With 'Arirang'Top Disaster Response Official Claims He Teleported to a Waffle House  Snoop Dogg had awild two weeksin Paris covering the Olympics for NBC.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3025, \"end\": 3037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waffle_House\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Waffle House\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waffle_House\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Waffle_House\"}, {\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 3072, \"end\": 3077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992865014, \"rank\": 7.13590219448245e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3104, \"end\": 3107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999993634082537, \"rank\": 4.465963654483652e-07, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right before the conclusion of the games, hegifted Simone Biles' dada Death Row gold chain for his 75th birthday.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3160, \"end\": 3172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 3179, \"end\": 3188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death_Row_Records\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.04836338473269e-13, \"text\": \"Death Row\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death_Row_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death_Row_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This story was updated 8/16/24 with a few more quotes from Dr. Dre about his Snoop Dogg's new album.\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3301, \"end\": 3311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://db